items.title: Hyundai Motor names Jose Munoz as CEO, first foreign leader
items.description: The Spanish-born Munoz replaces Jaehoon Chang, who is being promoted to vice-chairman of Hyundai’s automotive division, the company said in a statement Friday.

items.title: Nikhil Kamath's WTFund, Nazara Tech to back two gaming startups
items.description: Through this investment, Norian Games and Xigma Games will gain financial support, and access to mentorship and strategic guidance.

items.title: Glenmark Pharmaceuticals PAT at Rs 354 crore in September quarter
items.description: The company reported a consolidated loss after tax of Rs 180.3 crore in the same quarter last fiscal, Glenmark Pharmaceuticals said in a regulatory filing
